originalText.text: I have been going there a few years for Velashape and will now switch to the Venus Freeze. I was always seen promptly and most of the technicians seemed competent. I was not overcharged and I was surprised to read some of the negative reviews. I did have trouble locating the entrance the first time, I entered through the gynecologists office, but that was not a problem after the first time. The online scheduling is easy and they are open 7 days.

originalText.text: Dr. Goldstein's work demonstrates the value of having a seasoned physician as the practitioner.  The botox and other fillers were done so precisely that I was able to have benefit of the products without losing my natural  facial expressions. I had previously been afraid of "looking fake".  He did an amazing job! Recommend him highly!
